<rss xmlns:atom="http://www.w3.org/2005/Atom" version="2.0"><channel><title>系统设计 - 标签 - Schaepher's Blog</title><link>https://schaepher.github.io/tags/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/</link><description>系统设计 - 标签 - Schaepher's Blog</description><generator>Hugo -- gohugo.io</generator><language>zh-CN</language><lastBuildDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 11:39:00 +0000</lastBuildDate><atom:link href="https://schaepher.github.io/tags/%E7%B3%BB%E7%BB%9F%E8%AE%BE%E8%AE%A1/" rel="self" type="application/rss+xml"/><item><title>高内聚与低耦合</title><link>https://schaepher.github.io/2020/04/26/high-cohesion-low-coupling/</link><pubDate>Sun, 26 Apr 2020 11:39:00 +0000</pubDate><author>xxxx</author><guid>https://schaepher.github.io/2020/04/26/high-cohesion-low-coupling/</guid><description><![CDATA[<p>面向对象设计需要尽可能地符合高内聚与低耦合。它们的视角分为模块内部（内聚）和模块之间（耦合）。</p>
<p>模块内部各元素应紧密结合，一个模块只做一件事。</p>
<p>模块之间应该尽量独立，不直接产生依赖。</p>]]></description></item></channel></rss>